        "created_at": "2020-02-21T21:05:46.755Z",
        "cooked": "<p>It sounds good to me from the new restore system perspective.</p>\n<p>The only thing in my mind, which you may have considered, is that restore can restore to multiple key-ranges (maybe in parallel). So your layer may need to be aware of that as well.</p>",
